-- QUIPS: quoted forms

=== quip of word | 80
'x

=== quip of tight form | 80
'a.b

=== quip in expression | 80
f 'x y

=== quip of parens | 80
'(a + b)

=== quip of poem | 80
'+ a b

=== quip with tight rune | 80
'Quip;Semi

=== quip with trad | 80
'Quip"Trad"

=== nested quips | 80
'Quip 'Quip

=== quip of brackets | 80
'[b]

=== quip juxt | 80
('x(y))

=== quip in nest with infix | 80
(a, 'b, c)
---
(a , 'b , c)
